  <brief_title>Comparing Fixed-bearing Versus Mobile-bearing Prosthesis in Total Knee Arthroplasty: A Prospective Randomized Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Prosthesis in Total Knee Arthroplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
